Citation.sTitle: Octanol/Water Partition Coefficients of Sulfonamides: Experimental Determination and Calculation Using Physicochemical Descriptors
Citation.sAbstract: 1-Octanol/water partition coefficients log Kow of 38 sulfonamides were determined by the isothermal saturation method. These values were used both for direct correlation and as test data for the verification of a regression equation for calculation of log Kow on the basis of two physicochemical descriptors (molecular polarizability, a surrogate for molecular size, and H-bond acceptor ability). Comparison of experimental and calculated Kow values demonstrated the wide applicability of those equations.
